freebsd-utils (6.0-2.really.5.4-0.1) unreleased; urgency=low

  * Bump version to this ugly mess in order to provide an upgrade path on
    kfreebsd-amd64.  Hopefuly we'll get back to normal versioning when 5.x is
    no longer supported.
